Command-Line options
command              Action
vi file              Invoke vi on file
vi file1 file1       Invoke vi in fukes sequentially
view file            Invoke vi on file in read-only mode
vi-Rfile             Onvoke vi on file in read-only mode
vi-rfile             Recover file and recent edits after a crash
vi-t tag             Look up tag and start editing at its definition
vi-wn                Set the window size to useful over a slow connection
vi+file              Open file a last line
vi+n file            Open file directly at line number n

